{"tid":1165452,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"係咪火牛有事?","createTime":"2019-05-21T20:10:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-21T21:19:01.000Z","uid":140322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4b62e9a4e0c379ca06d2a61763f2f134ddf7fa0e","tid":1165452,"uid":140322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T20:10:53.000Z","msg":"話說最近幾日部機有時會無啦啦熄左重開<br />\n都有試過藍mon<br />\n今日發現打monhunt都係唔夠一陣就死<br />\n開頭諗緊係咪冇清塵 cpu過熱<br />\n用intel XTU check住個package temperature<br />\n開monhunt到卡死畫面死機個時係60度<br />\n而家諗緊係display card過熱定係火牛壞or拖板/電源供電唔夠<br />\n<br />\n因為隻牛用左差唔多成11年都冇事，諗緊係咪瓜柴<br />\n但係部機突然熄重開個時，冇聽到火牛有任何聲，同埋keep住開到機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edc8924a73d807d16b1754c6f94976e8c9df6bea","tid":1165452,"uid":199727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T20:58:35.000Z","msg":"火牛用左十一年 <br />\n比籍口自己換啦"},{"pid":"261d5670b9a09d73eb9d638112e472aa71ad6a46","tid":1165452,"uid":143411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T21:19:01.000Z","msg":"揾其他零件換下咪知咩事囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又有藉口換火牛啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}